<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Hinna Lampi</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Ngaite &quot;Hinna lampi ka bawl&quot; A tii,
 Khawvel ah hehpih leh nunnuom a;
 I len nangun lopina a kawih zo tai.

[V2]
 Aw Angel vam leh Lalchutphah a ngui zo tai,
 Pakna kingkang, chawihatna phaiphuleng;
 Aw lopnina a chawlzo tau,
 Lal nunnem in kalvari ah thuok in a tan tai.

[V3]
 2. Aw, Pathien cha, hukdampa chun ngaite,
 Kalvari leh thing hansiedawl ah;
 I gitloh ziekun thuokin, A chawzo tai.

[V4]
 3. Van leh khawvel haw hin hesuok leu chu;
 Hukdampa dangchak leh thavai chu;
 Kalvari tang hung naiin, ka lunggil ah.

[V5]
 4. Aw, ei puiin Thagau zie tang achun,
 Pathien Belam No thawmhau tak chun;
 &quot;Aw ka cha, ka kawmah hungin&quot; tin ei sam.

[V6]
 5. Lalpa, Na lam bawlah ei pui inla,
 Gamgaw ka mauna gam ngai puong ie;
 Na mel enin ziechun lengkhawm chiet tang kau.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>44</hymn_number>
</song>